paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT rf.*, lr.*, mlp.*
FROM (
select round(incentive, 4) AS incentive, avg(prob_p) AS rf_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS rf_prob_3, avg(actual_p) AS rf_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS rf_actual_3
from rf_pred 
GROUP BY round(incentive, 4)
) rf
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
select round(incentive, 4) AS incentive, avg(prob_p) AS lr_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS lr_prob_3, avg(actual_p) AS lr_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS lr_actual_3
from lr_pred 
GROUP BY round(incentive, 4)
) lr ON lr.incentive = rf.incentive
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
select round(incentive, 4) AS incentive, avg(prob_p) AS mlp_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS mlp_prob_3, avg(actual_p) AS mlp_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS mlp_actual_3
from mlp_pred 
GROUP BY round(incentive, 4)
) mlp ON mlp.incentive = rf.incentive
ORDER BY rf.incentive

SELECT rf.*, lr.*, mlp.*
FROM (
select age, sum(prob_p) AS rf_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS rf_prob_3, sum(actual_p) AS rf_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS rf_actual_3
from rf_pred 
GROUP BY age
) rf
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
select age, sum(prob_p) AS lr_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS lr_prob_3, avg(actual_p) AS lr_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS lr_actual_3
from lr_pred 
GROUP BY age
) lr ON lr.age = rf.age
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
select age, sum(prob_p) AS mlp_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS mlp_prob_3, avg(actual_p) AS mlp_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS mlp_actual_3
from mlp_pred 
GROUP BY age
) mlp ON mlp.age = rf.age
ORDER BY rf.age
